3bhk beachfront villa at ECR
*Pricing for 6 guests,  additional guests are chargeable at 1200 per adult,  500 per kid* *Saturday rates are higher at minimum 10,000 for 8 guests*

*SUMMARY*
3bhk beachhouse at ECR, CHENNAI with a private beach,  just next door to fishermen's village.  

Great views and beach access with 25 member seating,  garden area and large plot for big event too.

*DESCRIPTION*
Spacious, breezy oceanfront 3bhk large 2800 sq ft villa built before tsunami and stands strong to sea salt and moisture overcoming the waves, the sun,  corrosion and a lot more!

What we love about our home is that the design allows 100% air circulation, ventilation and keeps the home cool at all times after 4pm as the sun sets on the other end allowing the sea breeze to cool the home down. We have a fridge, lots of furniture to handle upto 20 guests and power back up. 

3 attached baths,  a large furnished living and dining with French windows opening into the spacious balcony having witnessed many movie shootings and weddings.

2 rooms are A/C fitted, but the seafacing room with French windows doesn't have an AC because it's a really chilly room after 4pm due to the cold natural cooling by the SEA BREEZE.

9r9Fz6xpcq8.description:
In this video i have explained the new plans of jio, airtel, vodafone/idea, Bsnl and which is the best according to the plans and the needs

Kindly checkout!!! Hope it wil be helpful for you to choose the right plan and save some money!!.

The reason behind telecoms increasing traffis ::

 Telecoms license fee or spectrum usage charges is calculated based on their revenue.. Government while evaluating a Telecoms revenue is not just including the revenue from network service it provides to the customer but it is also including the revenue generated by other activities like sale and purchase of assets, bonds, shares etc.. but according to telecom company total revenue should be calculated only from the money it is generating from network service and not other revenues.. for several years the companies have been under rating their revenue in audit books... When govt found it they have asked to pay the spectrum charges arising from other revenues also along with penalty... This will cause huge loss in Telecom so they have raised traiffs... 🙂..
